subject: Baseball
Playoff Games
lead_paragraph: Yankees go with a three-man rotation of C. C. Sabathia, Andy Pettitte and Phil Hughes, leaving A.J. Burnett as a reliever and Javier Vazquez off the 11-man pitching staff.
